    "Wang Mang usurped power from the Emperor, declared himself Emperor, and established the Xin Dynasty.",
    "He attempted to implement ambitious reforms to land ownership and taxation, but this led to widespread revolt.",
    "These revolts, coupled with natural disasters and economic difficulties, led to the downfall of the Xin Dynasty.",
    "Wang Mang was killed during the rebellion that ended his rule.",
    "The Han Dynasty was then restored."
